*Mesec* je prirodni satelit Zemlje. (The Moon is the natural satellite of the Earth.)
Mesečev svet je prekriven prazninama. (The Moon's surface is covered with craters.)
Kako *mesec* mesečevo svetlo? (How does the Moon light the night?)
Dok se *mesec* okreće oko Zemlje, njegov izgled se menja. (As the Moon orbits around the Earth, its appearance changes.)
Kada se *mesec* nalazi između Zemlje i Sunca, on se oseća kao da je Sunce u senci. (When the Moon is between the Earth and the Sun, it feels like the Sun is in the shade.)